### FinMind Auth API — Test Commands (curl)
### Use these to verify the backend is working correctly.

### ───────────────────────────────────────────
### 1. Health Check
### ───────────────────────────────────────────
# curl http://localhost:5000/

### ───────────────────────────────────────────
### 2. Register a new user
### ───────────────────────────────────────────
# curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"email": "test@finmind.com", "password": "password123"}' \
#   -c cookies.txt

### ───────────────────────────────────────────
### 3. Login
### ───────────────────────────────────────────
# curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"email": "test@finmind.com", "password": "password123"}' \
#   -c cookies.txt

### ───────────────────────────────────────────
### 4. Refresh Token (uses cookie)
### ───────────────────────────────────────────
# curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/refresh \
#   -b cookies.txt

### ───────────────────────────────────────────
### 5. Get Current User (protected — needs access token)
### Replace <ACCESS_TOKEN> with the token from login/register.
### ───────────────────────────────────────────
# curl http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>"

### ───────────────────────────────────────────
### 6. Logout
### ───────────────────────────────────────────
# curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/logout \
#   -b cookies.txt

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════
### TRANSACTION ENDPOINTS (Phase 2)
### All require Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════

### ───────────────────────────────────────────
### 7. Create Transaction (AI-categorized)
### ───────────────────────────────────────────
# curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/transactions \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>" \
#   -d '{"amount": 250, "description": "Uber ride to airport"}'

### ───────────────────────────────────────────
### 8. Get All Transactions
### ───────────────────────────────────────────
# curl http://localhost:5000/api/transactions \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>"

### ───────────────────────────────────────────
### 9. Delete a Transaction
### Replace <TRANSACTION_ID> with a real ID.
### ───────────────────────────────────────────
# curl -X DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/transactions/<TRANSACTION_ID> \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>"
